parameters:
Henchman: At least... make it so he doesn't suffer
anymore... Ugh... Please, ease my brother's pain, I beg
you... uuu...
Henchman: Miss... what about the boss...?
I couldn't do it...
Henchman: No way...

Indeed, as you say, making sure he doesn't suffer might be a
form of mercy.

But I couldn't bring myself to believe that was the right
thing to do...

Henchman: To see the boss in such a state, it's just too
much...

Indeed, the result that has befallen him is unbearable to
witness.
But just as much, we must not give up hope.

If magic experiments have caused this, then perhaps magic
could also be the key to restoring his original form, might
it not?

Henchman: But... until we find a way, the boss will remain
like that?!
You! You must believe in him!!

Is the man you deeply believe in really such a weak man? No,
that can't be right!!!

If you care about him, then you must believe! Believe in his
strength! In his tenacity to survive until now!! And in a
future where you can laugh together as comrades once more!!!
Henchman: Ugh! Uuuuuh...!!

It's true, you may be villains! But this should not be
allowed! Do not succumb to misfortune! Do not go with the
easy flow! Choose to live on, no matter how dirty the path!

Just as you have lived through everything with him until
now!

Henchman: Uuuuh...!! That's right...! The boss was dirtier
and more stubborn than anyone...! And yet, what was I
thinking...!!

You're not at fault. Your feelings for him were just too
strong, that's all.

Henchman: But... how do we find a way to turn the boss back
to normal...

Don't worry. Who do you think I am? I am Reisha, a knight
from the royal capital Near Lake. I will lend you my
strength. If we scour the entire capital and that's not
enough, then we'll search beyond our borders.

Once his case is resolved, you all will properly atone for
your crimes. Once your atonement is complete, then you can
rely on me again. Let's work together to make this country
better!

Henchman: Ughuuu! I'm sorry...! So sorry...!! Uuugh!!
Uuuuuuh...!!

Ah! As expected of your boss!

Received "Dust Repellent." Received "Elixir of Tiares."

prevent any further sacrifices.

true...!!

parameters: Thug Minion: Hey, you there!!

Are you one of the thugs who attacked the shops in the
reconstruction district?! Why are you here...?!

Thug Minion: I'll explain later! It's the boss! He's been
taken to the lab by these researchers!!
What did you say?!?

Thug Minion: Please! I apologize for what happened before! I
know I have no right to ask this of you!

Thug Minion: But right now, you're the only one I can turn
to! Please!! Save my boss!!

Thug Minion: One of our guys has already been turned into
experimental material! No one who's taken to that room ever
comes back!!

Thug Minion: I'm begging you! Please save my boss...!!
Please!!
Damn it!! Where is that place? Tell me quickly!
Thug Minion: I think it's just down this road!!
I'm on it!
Thug Minion: Please! Help my boss!!
Thug Minion: Please! Help my boss!!
